						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab built into the ceiling of the left maṇḍapa of the eastern gōpura of the Vīranārāyaṇasvāmi temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record of about the <hi rend="bold">11th century A.D.</hi> seems to record a grant of and made by <hi rend="bold">Bāyikabbe to Chidaṇṇa.</hi> The grant of <hi rend="italic">bhaṭṭa-vṛitti</hi> and <hi rend="italic">chhātra-vṛitti</hi> are also recorded.</p>						

						</summary>
